Package: RcTools
Title: A Collection of Report Card Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Shand", , "adamshand22@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package makes a collection of Report Card functions available to the technical team of the Northern Three Partnerships. Tools are mostly focused on styling tabular outputs for inclusion in the Technical Report, this includes conditional formatting, assigning grades, and cell colouring.
